# Instructions
# ===========================================
# 1. Copy this file: cp env.template .env.local
# 2. Update FOOTBALL_DATA_API_KEY with your paid API key
# 3. Restart your development server: npm run dev
# 4. Test the connection: curl http://localhost:3000/api/health
# 5. Run data sync: curl -X POST "http://localhost:3000/api/sync?action=full"

